commit.message:
builtins.def (gamma, lgamma): Use ATTR_MATHFN_FPROUNDING_STORE.

	* builtins.def (gamma, lgamma): Use ATTR_MATHFN_FPROUNDING_STORE.
	
testsuite:
	* gcc.dg/torture/builtin-attr-1.c: Don't test gamma/lgamma.
	* gcc.dg/torture/builtin-convert-1.c: Don't test lgamma.

From-SVN: r118366
